{"tid":2012053,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"7個傳媒工會促警遏止對記者施襲　冀緊急約見鄧炳強","createTime":"2020-05-11T11:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T12:16:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dd8134fccdfd3e3d1db97e90a7431d7df31c899e","tid":2012053,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:55:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525532-20200511.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525532-20200511.htm&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=fe01ec36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525532-20200511.htm&h=ee4b6855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525532-20200511.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n7個傳媒工會發表聯署聲明，要求警方就昨晚在旺角的行動，緊急約見警務處處長鄧炳強，並要求警方立即遏止警隊針對記者施襲的歪風，將失控的警務人員停職調查。<br />\n<br />\n香港記者協會、香港攝影記者協會、香港電台節目製作人員工會、獨立評論人協會、大專教育工作者聯席、明報職工協會，及壹傳媒工會共7個傳媒工會，批評政府及警方聲稱尊重傳媒作為第四權，實際上卻千方百計打壓。警方昨晚在旺角驅散人群期間，藉故多番截查正在進行採訪工作的記者，更強迫他們向着警方的錄影機讀出姓名、身份證號碼及所屬機構名稱等，喝令記者蹲下及禁止繼續拍攝，並近距離向記者的眼、耳等噴射胡椒噴劑。更有報道指，有記者被箍頸近20秒，認為是對新聞工作者極盡羞辱，令同業義憤填膺。<br />\n<br />\n聯署強調，新聞工作者一直保持克制、忍耐，無意與警方為敵，但包容絕不能變成縱容，籲警務人員勿忘要以「正直及誠實的品格」、「專業精神」等服務社會的承諾。"},{"pid":"a2ea646bde32c79dc941a4f36c8e957e79265937","tid":2012053,"uid":320192,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:56:30.000Z","msg":"雪糕筒 Airbnb 自導自演 僭建 冰毒 曲解法律 老屈<br />\n煩請記者朋友追問一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n辛苦晒記者朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d482512ba3ac17f573cf2dca88269677c2006c24","tid":2012053,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:57:10.000Z","msg":"係鄧炳強落ORDER要小心唔好俾記者影到架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88687732e5e702c35d5a637a3187b3c0b2caf6e5","tid":2012053,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:01:56.000Z","msg":"頗天真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係鄧炳強同意, 細個班邊會敢咁癲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4657c2bfd33725f42f1696cc3ae47d86485a94c5","tid":2012053,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:02:21.000Z","msg":"停職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e806993d39f68f5ebc2616a1d7a43bbd17139a","tid":2012053,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"關機打記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97930e2dde45c5b555a4278d7d74034ea218274","tid":2012053,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:03:06.000Z","msg":"警: 第四權? 基本法有寫架?"},{"pid":"2d2ce7e65335de6b640517ee61969db056428e0b","tid":2012053,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:04:07.000Z","msg":"約見？？<br />\n佢落order架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傻撚左？"},{"pid":"22cbfa96c507fe5b3204db136ece06bc150d0525","tid":2012053,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d2ce7e65335de6b640517ee61969db056428e0b","tid":2012053,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:04:07.000Z","msg":"約見？？<br />\n佢落order架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傻撚左？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:05:03.000Z","msg":"鄧就係賊王"},{"pid":"adfcd920f54b6e6ee64b36968dd78446e4b148fb","tid":2012053,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:06:58.000Z","msg":"聽日去元朗區議會見佢"},{"pid":"da7479b8562718a6fceafee9b6216593cca12ee7","tid":2012053,"uid":52675,